  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the immediate therapeutic efficacies of Gufoni maneuver and mastoid oscillation
      in apogeotropic type of benign paroxysmal positional vertigo involving the horizontal
      semicircular canal (HC-BPPV), a randomized, prospective, sham-controlled study was
      conducted.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
